# CODEOWNERS - Automatic PR Review Assignment
#
# This file defines code ownership for automatic pull request review assignment.
# When @copilot creates a PR, the specified owners are automatically requested as reviewers.
#
# Format: pattern @username
# Docs: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default owner for all files
# All PRs will be auto-assigned to @owner for human review
* @owner

# Future refinements (examples - commented out):
# /docs/ @owner @tech-writer
# /.github/ @owner @devops-team
# /tests/ @owner @qa-team
